{"lastModified":1760019735795,"uri":"c::18277099312::vessel::281bc6d0-a84a-11ef-9dd4-8f5d2a2cbca2","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nThe Lagoon 51 is a sophisticated 2025 model catamaran that accommodates up to 11 guests in 7 double cabins, each with its own en-suite bathroom. Additionally, it offers space for 2 adults or 4 children in smaller inner cabins without bathrooms. A crew cabin and head are located in the bow, and if you choose to hire a hostess or chef, one of the inner cabins can be designated for them.\n\nThis Lagoon 51 model is designed to seamlessly blend indoor and outdoor living. The spacious saloon, inviting flybridge, and expansive aft and forward cockpits create the perfect setting for relaxation. You can join the professional skipper during sailing or simply enjoy time with family and friends on the modular seating of the flybridge. The large transoms provide safe and easy access to the dock or water, while the forward cockpit offers stunning, unobstructed sea views.\n\nThe Lagoon 51 is fully equipped with a generator, inverter, air conditioning, heating, watermaker, ice maker, TV with DVD, Fusion Apollo audio system with cockpit speakers, and Wi-Fi. For added comfort, the flybridge and cockpit are shaded by sun covers, complemented by cushions and a cockpit shower. The hydraulic platform, complete with a 20 hp outboard engine for the tender, simplifies launching the dinghy and transforms into a private beach onboard. The galley is fully equipped with a freezer, coffee maker, dishwasher, microwave, and stove with oven, ensuring a fully convenient and enjoyable sailing experience.","blueprint":{"name":"REALITY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::281bc6d0-a84a-11ef-9dd4-8f5d2a2cbca2::assets::c31b5ac0-a84e-11ef-b86b-736c7451fe64/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::281bc6d0-a84a-11ef-9dd4-8f5d2a2cbca2::assets::c317b140-a84e-11ef-ac61-53b93ad88f1a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a